0RoOkY_QRl8Yy2oMkJAodsY_W7_GnMHXspVw3fuuBpiYA7JlSOlY/s220/SH+Kruh+s+dlznom1.JPG"}}],"generator":{"version":"7.00","uri":"http://www.blogger.com","$t":"Blogger"},"openSearch$startIndex":{"$t":"1"},"openSearch$itemsPerPage":{"$t":"25"},"entry":[{"id":{"$t":"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-6818054921907446479.post-1629604656182790796"},"published":{"$t":"2017-10-05T07:08:00.001+02:00"},"updated":{"$t":"2017-10-08T20:59:32.911+02:00"},"title":{"type":"text","$t":"Prednáška o Keltoch - Video"},"content":{"type":"html","$t":"<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\nDňa 5. 10. 2017 sme spolu s Dwarf digital archeology a SNM zorganizovali prednášku pracovníkov Slovenského národného múzea Radoslava Čambala a Mareka Budaja na tému Kelti na juhozápadnom Slovensku. Celú prednášku sme vysielali naživo a môžete si ju pozrieť aj zo záznamu na</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<br /></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/dwarfdigital/videos/1976870849255078/\" target=\"_blank\">TOMTO ODKAZE</a></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<br /></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<br /></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<br /></div>\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi1B4Tqp26URB8ZmnWLzolh8CxpgZVC1R-pVtZw5OC93WRQ2sTLRQEYwewISofBP_yDRC8ZdanIlq7useK2-kubzht9foUMire5hSauOiMRJ9LLY6ug-7_aD3WLCEDitjGzhmgo6ll2900/s1600/21994206_1973656746243155_8864288541291012470_o.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"900\" data-original-width=\"1440\" height=\"200\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi1B4Tqp26URB8ZmnWLzolh8CxpgZVC1R-pVtZw5OC93WRQ2sTLRQEYwewISofBP_yDRC8ZdanIlq7useK2-kubzht9foUMire5hSauOiMRJ9LLY6ug-7_aD3WLCEDitjGzhmgo6ll2900/s320/21994206_1973656746243155_8864288541291012470_o.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<br /><br />V stredu 5.10.2017 ste v Tvrdošovciach okrem prednášky o Keltoch, ktorú sme vysielali online, mohli vidieť aj výstavu s názvom Podivuhodný keltský ľud, ktorú nám zapožičala Univerzita Konštantína filozofa v Nitre. Návštevníci si tiež mohli pozrieť niekoľko zapožičaných nálezov z keltského obdobia a vychutnať si vytlačené vizualizácie keltskej osady od Dwarf digital vo veľkom formáte.  Samozrejme, tiež bola možnosť osobne sa porozprávať s archeológmi Radoslavom Čambalom, Igorom Bazovským, Martinom Furmanom, ako aj s numizmatikom Marekom Budajom.</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgPqXxcTbza77AwqsrOuj4E9Ps-4VX1ZGeuC4LvD4e1uzxWE2jvaaO1ynWi3iZBDybkVA_xH-w6TaTzky2QMCvbGWN3ffMOksvvcDrU2-HMF6RiY1_UguY9yzTEEogi7WgvlDnHut1eED4/s1600/22228431_371801323242531_630063247556923745_n.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"576\" data-original-width=\"960\" height=\"192\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgPqXxcTbza77AwqsrOuj4E9Ps-4VX1ZGeuC4LvD4e1uzxWE2jvaaO1ynWi3iZBDybkVA_xH-w6TaTzky2QMCvbGWN3ffMOksvvcDrU2-HMF6RiY1_UguY9yzTEEogi7WgvlDnHut1eED4/s320/22228431_371801323242531_630063247556923745_n.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<br />\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjHlW8cZJ4EY15KDzPsNg_1kiLEQovnYhrfzlO_GxgcUj6FjYUgM9dtcuN-SSUwSvoeQVvW_BhycVLaSfArEzBbsKz9wO7ZIoKxXjBxCma6va7VDbhqmUdevcxGXqeGCql3n6t0DGSNpmE/s1600/22228438_371801313242532_6182430190531085853_n.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"422\" data-original-width=\"960\" height=\"140\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29